SchemaBuilderFactory (autotransform.schema.factory)

A simple factory for producing SchemaBuilders from their type.

class autotransform.schema.factory.SchemaBuilderFactory

Bases: object

The factory class for SchemaBuilders. Maps a type to a SchemaBuilder.

_map

A mapping from SchemaBuilderType to the associated class.

Type

Dict[SchemaBuilderType, Type[SchemaBuilder]]

static get(builder_type: autotransform.schema.type.SchemaBuilderType) → autotransform.schema.builder.SchemaBuilder

Simple get method using the _map attribute.

Parameters

builder_type (SchemaBuilderType) – The type of a SchemaBuilder.

Returns

An instance of the associated SchemaBuilder.

Return type

SchemaBuilder
